findings.title: Change Taxes
findings.description: The constants maxBuyTaxes, maxSellTaxes, and maxTransferTaxes are set to 1500, which may allow an owner to change taxes arbitrarily.

findings.title: Cannot exceed maximums
findings.description: The smart contract has constants defined for maxBuyTaxes, maxSellTaxes, maxTransferTaxes, and maxRoundtripTax which could lead to potential issues if exceeded.

findings.title: Cannot exceed roundtrip maximum
findings.description: The contract has a constant 'maxRoundtripTax' set to 2000, implying that there is a restriction on exceeding this value.
